&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;ERROR&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Failed to execute goal org.apache.maven.plugins:maven-compiler-plugin:2.1:testCompile (default-testCompile) on project commons-math: Compilation failure: Compilation failure:&lt;br/&gt;
